hokku-server (2.1.1-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * Upload/delete endpoints return JSON error responses on filesystem
    failures (e.g. systemd ProtectSystem read-only mounts) instead of
    Flask HTML error pages, so the web GUI can show a useful message.
  * Web GUI: image grid shows every uploaded file, with a "Generating
    preview" badge on entries still being dithered.
